WEBVTT

00:00:00.576 --> 00:00:02.048
A column of bones called

00:00:02.040 --> 00:00:03.960
vertebrae make up your spine.

00:00:04.112 --> 00:00:06.032
Spinal instrumentation

00:00:06.056 --> 00:00:08.456
is a surgical procedure to stabilize

00:00:08.450 --> 00:00:09.984
or strengthen the vertebrae

00:00:09.980 --> 00:00:13.344
through attachment of rods, hooks, or wires.

00:00:13.448 --> 00:00:15.384
This procedure may be performed

00:00:15.380 --> 00:00:17.984
because of broken vertebra, or arthritis,

00:00:17.980 --> 00:00:19.608
or spinal weakening due to

00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:22.496
birth defects, diseases, or tumors.

